><span dir="ltr">美體雕塑：Liposonix立塑無創溶脂、電波美體緊實療程、瘦小腿、</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#2f4f4f"><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Reaction_燃脂電波。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style="color:#2f4f4f"><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr">其他服務：煥儷動力光治療、專業術後修護。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="color:#2f4f4f">了解更多煥儷美形：</span><ins><a href="http://w2.rebeauty.com.tw/articles/5"><span style="color:#3399ff">醫師團隊</span></a></ins><span style="color:rgb(47, 79, 79)"> / </span><ins><a href="http://w2.rebeauty.com.tw/articles/6"><span style="color:#3399ff">門診時間</span></a></ins><span style="color:rgb(47, 79, 79)"> / </span><ins><a href="http://w2.rebeauty.com.tw/articles/7"><span style="color:#3399ff">環境設備</span></a></ins></span></span></p>\r\n', '1', '2013-08-15', 1, 1, 611, 'tw', 33, '', '', '', '2014-02-24 19:18:23', '2014-10-22 08:02:22'),
