(32, '海外貴賓赴台醫美', '<h1><span style="color:#3399cc"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif"><samp>海外貴賓赴台醫美</samp></span></span></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#2f4f4f"><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif"><samp>煥儷美形集結了專業醫療團隊及芳療保養，讓您安心放心享受美麗蛻變的過程。</samp></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#2f4f4f"><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif"><samp>歡迎海外貴賓親臨煥儷，感受煥儷尊爵的服務。</samp></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#2f4f4f"><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif"><samp>&nbsp;</samp></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif"><span style="color:#3399cc"><span style="font-size:18px">海外貴賓赴台流程：</span></span></span></strong><br />\r\n<span style="color:#2f4f4f"><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif"><samp>STEP1.至煥儷美形診所官網&nbsp;<br />\r\nSTEP2.留下您的預約資料 <ins>請按此</ins><br />\r\nSTEP3.我們會有專人與您聯繫，確認資料並完成預約&nbsp;<br />\r\nSTEP4.來台進行治療&nbsp;<br />\r\nSTEP5.術後衛教&nbsp;<br />\r\nSTEP6.預約回診時間&nbsp;</samp></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<samp><strong><span style="color:#3399cc"><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif">煥儷美形營業時間：</span></span></span></strong></samp><span style="color:#3399cc"><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif"><samp>&nbsp;</samp></span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#2f4f4f"><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif"><samp>週一至週六：10:30-20:30 (每周日公休)&nbsp;<br />\r\n關於整形美容的療程項目、價格及預約...等等，都歡迎您透過以下的方式聯繫我們。&nbsp;</samp></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#2f4f4f"><span style="font-family:monospace; font-size:16px">網站預約系統：請按此</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#2f4f4f"><span style="font-size:16px"><span style="font-